观看“Weird Al”Yankovic 和 Will Forte 翻唱 Chappell Roan 的“Hot To Go!”在慈善音乐会上https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-weird-al-yankovic-and-will-forte-cover-chappell-roans-hot-to-go-at-benefit-concert-3811374?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-weird-al-yankovic-and-will-forte-cover-chappell-roans-hot-to-go-at-benefit-concertMax Pilley Sun, 10 Nov 2024 19:41:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3811374 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这场表演是在 Jason Sudeikis 的年度“Thundergong！”上进行的。堪萨斯城慈善活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-weird-al-yankovic-and-will-forte-cover-chappell-roans-hot-to-go-at-benefit-concert-3811374">观看“Weird Al”Yankovic 和 Will Forte 翻唱 Chappell Roan 的“Hot To Go!”慈善音乐会</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/weird_al_forte-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/weird-al-yankovic">“Weird Al”Yankovic</a>和 Will Forte 忠实演绎了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a>的“Hot To Go!”周六（11 月 9 日）在堪萨斯城举行的一场慈善音乐会上。</p><p>演出是在一年一度的雷锣期间进行的！该演出在该市的上城区剧院举行，该剧院由<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/ted-lasso"><i>泰德·拉索 (Ted Lasso)</i></a>明星杰森·苏戴奇斯 (Jason Sudeikis) 组织，并支持<a href="https://www.stepsoffaithfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“信仰之步”(Steps of Faith)</a>慈善机构，该慈善机构帮助截肢患者安装假肢。</p><p>因<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><i>《周六夜现场》</i></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-lego-movie"><i>《乐高大电影》</i></a>而闻名的演员兼喜剧演员福尔特在介绍这首歌时向扬科维奇建议，他们应该直接播放这首歌，而不是采用后者通常的模仿风格。</p><p> “你以采用流行歌曲并改变歌词而闻名，但如果我们现在唱一首流行歌曲，但我们没有改变歌词呢？”福尔特说道。</p><p> “不改歌词吗？多么新颖的概念啊，这是个好主意。让我们开始吧，”扬科维奇回答道。</p><p>在这里观看他们版本的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">中西部公主的兴衰</a>》剪辑，包括必要的舞蹈动作： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="“马上出发！” （Chappell Roan 封面） • “Weird Al”Yankovic 和 Will Forte • 雷鸣！ 2024年" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KaiyQ7jJMaI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>还上雷功！ Bill 是 Sudeikis 本人，他翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wings">Wings</a>的《Live And Let Die》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的《Happier Than Ever》，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/public-enemy">Public Enemy</a>的《Bring The Noise》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/flavor-flav">Flavor Flav</a>的一个版本，您可以在这里看到： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="雷公2024！ Flavor Flav 和 Jason Sudeikis 演唱了 Anthrax 和 Public Enemy 的《Bring the Noise》。" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v9tHhJOn7rc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>罗恩目前正蒸蒸日上，本周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-parts-ways-with-management-team-3811268">获得了格莱美所有四个主要类别的提名</a>：年度专辑、年度唱片、年度歌曲和最佳新人。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-parts-ways-with-management-team-3811268">她还与她的管理团队 State Of The Art 分离</a>，自 2018 年起一直由他们代表。</p><p>罗恩是<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><i>《周六夜现场</i></a>》最近一集（11 月 2 日）的音乐嘉宾， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-debuts-new-lesbian-anthem-country-song-on-snl-3809048">她在节目中首次推出了一首新乡村歌曲“The Giver”，一些歌迷已将其称为“女同性恋赞歌”</a> 。</p><p>这是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-seemingly-teases-new-album-its-time-for-a-hot-new-bombshell-3807708">Roan 调侃她备受期待的第二张专辑</a>之后。上个月，她在 Instagram 上分享了一篇帖子，其中提到了<i>《爱情岛》</i> ，暗示即将推出的项目。</p><p>在轮播帖子中，她举起了她的首张专辑，帖子中的另一张幻灯片显示她手里拿着麦克风，似乎在录音室里。她在标题中写道：“在我看来，专辑有点突然，但现在是时候欢迎一个热门的新炸弹进入别墅了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-weird-al-yankovic-and-will-forte-cover-chappell-roans-hot-to-go-at-benefit-concert-3811374">观看“Weird Al”Yankovic 和 Will Forte 翻唱 Chappell Roan 的“Hot To Go!”慈善音乐会</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
艾玛·斯通因侮辱杰西·艾森伯格而获得“僵尸之地”角色https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-stone-got-zombieland-role-by-insulting-jesse-eisenberg-3811368?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=emma-stone-got-zombieland-role-侮辱杰西·艾森伯格Max PilleySun, 10 Nov 2024 18:50:56 +0000 Film NewsNewsComedy https://www.nme.com/?p=3811368 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “她离开了房间，我只觉得自己如此、如此渺小”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-stone-got-zombieland-role-by-insulting-jesse-eisenberg-3811368">艾玛·斯通因侮辱杰西·艾森伯格而获得“僵尸乐园”角色的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jesse_eisenberg_emma-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jesse-eisenberg">杰西·艾森伯格</a>透露，与<i>《僵尸之地》</i>搭档的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emma-stone">艾玛·斯通</a>在试镜时侮辱了他，从而获得了这个角色。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="657" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/zombieland-10-anniversary-recap-emma-stone-woody-harrelson-2554509"><b>10 岁的《僵尸之地》：仍然是僵尸电影中最有趣的</b></a></li></ul><p>这部 2009 年的末日喜剧由鲁本·弗莱舍 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/venom"><i>《毒液》</i></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/uncharted"><i>《神秘海域</i></a>》) 执导，艾森伯格饰演哥伦布，斯通饰演威奇托，这两位幸存者在僵尸横行的美国，试图展开一场漫长的越野公路旅行。伍迪·哈里森和阿比盖尔·布蕾斯琳联合主演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bill-murray">比尔·默里</a>也客串了令人难忘的一幕。</p><p>这部电影是斯通的突破时刻，艾森伯格在<a href="https://www.siriusxm.com/player/episode-audio/entity/6e47a993-cec8-41e3-5a42-362dd412a086" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>与杰西卡·肖一起出现在 SiriusXM 的《聚光灯》</i></a>中时回忆起，当其他竞争者选角威奇托这个角色时，她是如何立即从其他竞争者中脱颖而出的。</p><p> “我已经被选入这部电影，所以那天我像很多人一样试镜她的角色，”他说。 “当时的演员都是很棒的女演员，但他们都在努力融入电影，所以他们真的很有礼貌。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《僵尸之地》官方预告片 #1" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8m9EVP8X7N8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “然后[斯通]进来了，她开始在场景中取笑我，就像在场景中侮辱我一样，这太有趣了。他们是如此迅速、如此有趣、如此尖锐，”他补充道。 “她离开了房间，我感觉自己是如此、如此渺小。”</p><p> “我们当时想，‘天啊。那个人是个天才。也许试镜时她就已经 19 岁了。我的意思是，她确实是一个非常出色、异常聪明的人。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/zombieland-10-anniversary-recap-emma-stone-woody-harrelson-2554509">正如<i>NME</i>在电影上映 10 周年之际指出的那样</a>， <i>《僵尸乐园》</i> “为僵尸类型注入了创造性的乐趣、自我意识和血腥的黑色幽默。”</p><p> “虽然我们仍然对人类被某种召唤不死生物和食人瘟疫消灭的想法挥之不去的迷恋，但即使是在它在英国上映十周年之际， <i>《僵尸之地》</i>仍然可以说是任何人都能享受到的最有趣的游戏。僵尸片。”</p><p> 2019年，续集<i>《Zombieland: Double Tap</i> 》发布。 <i>《NME》</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/zombieland-double-tap-review-2557658">在一篇三星级评论中</a>指出：“不幸的是，随着事情的进展，一切都变得相当可预测。延长的战斗场景拖沓，玩笑变得不足为奇，每一个怀旧的参考都变得无聊。当我们得出不可避免的令人头脑混乱的结论时，一切都感觉很匆忙，充满了缺乏回报的戏剧性时刻。虽然核心演员注入了一些急需的能量，但这部电影似乎常常试图重现前作的魔力，而不是添加任何新东西。”</p><p>斯通凭借<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/la-la-land"><i>《爱乐之城》</i></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/poor-things-review-emma-stone-yorgos-lanthimos-sex-comedy-3569226#:~:text=With%20a%20cunning%20use%20of,big%20smile%20on%20their%20faces."><i>《可怜的东西》</i></a>两度获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>奖，而艾森伯格则执导了即将上映的喜剧片<i>《真正的痛苦</i>》，由基兰·卡尔金主演。这部电影讲述了两兄弟前往波兰探寻家族根源的故事， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jesse-eisenberg-opens-up-about-becoming-a-polish-citizen-3810735">艾森伯格最近几天也公开了自己想要成为波兰公民的故事</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-stone-got-zombieland-role-by-insulting-jesse-eisenberg-3811368">艾玛·斯通因侮辱杰西·艾森伯格而获得“僵尸乐园”角色的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
